metadata.description:
By TNCARTteam  
Who could possibly bring sizzle to the dull life of the Bored Ape Yacht Club (BAYC)? Meet the gorgeous ladies from the Lady Ape Club (LAC)!Discover our fabulous Lady Apes and grab the one that makes your heart skip a beat before others do! In fact, BAYC #5668 has already found the love of his life in the person of LAC #0!Join events exclusive to LAC members only. Check out our roadmap and join our community with awesome benefits! For more details, visit our website https://ladyapeclub.com
